      "acceptanceCriteria": "Experimental test conditions (flow rate, rotational speed, fluid viscosity, hematocrit) must match CFD boundary conditions within ±5%.",
      "rationale": "In-vitro test conditions documented in Morrison et al. (2017) match CFD boundary conditions within 2.1% for flow rate and 1.8% for rotational speed. Fluid properties (bovine blood analog, 33% hematocrit) replicated in material model."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Output comparison",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
