      "acceptanceCriteria": "Predicted RH index must agree with experimental measurements within ±15% across all 5 operating points.",
      "rationale": "CFD-predicted RH values agree with in-vitro measurements within 8.4% across all five flow-speed operating points. Maximum deviation observed at the lowest flow condition (3 LPM, 2500 RPM) at 8.4%. All predictions satisfy the ±15% acceptance criterion, achieving Gradation 3."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
